      "content": "To appear sophisticated in international business, prioritize impeccable grooming and tailored, high-quality clothing over flashy trends. Universally, conservative power dressing—think well-fitted suits in neutral colors for men, and sharp, elegant separates for women—signals reliability and respect. Focus on mastering non-verbal communication; this includes maintaining confident posture and practicing active, engaged listening to convey true professionalism. Always ensure your accessories and demeanor match the level of the business environment you are entering.",
