      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. so like, if i'm writing for people in places like singapore or dubai or even lagos, should they stick to those western suit/separates vibes to stay professional, or is it okay to incorporate more local styles? i want to make sure my readers don't look \"unprofessional\" just because they aren't wearing a blazer.",
