      "content": "While Western business attire provides a solid global baseline, adapting to local nuances is crucial for true sophistication. In conservative hubs like Dubai, maintaining traditional elements alongside professional tailoring is often wise. Elsewhere, subtle integration of high-quality local fabrics or silhouettes shows cultural awareness without sacrificing gravitas. The key is ensuring that any local incorporation maintains a polished, streamlined appearance rather than appearing casual or decorative.",
